=================================================================================
                        POWER OPTIMIZATION RECOMMENDATIONS
=================================================================================

1. Implement DSP block gating when interpolation not needed
   Estimated savings: 8.2 mW (during blanking period)

2. Reduce output driver swing for short PCB traces
   Estimated savings: 2.4 mW

3. Optimize line buffer memory access patterns
   Estimated savings: 1.8 mW

4. Add clock gating for unused logic during blanking
   Estimated savings: 3.6 mW

5. Reduce multiplier precision from 18x18 to 16x16
   Estimated savings: 2.1 mW

Total Potential Savings: 18.1 mW (7.7% reduction)
Optimized power: 216.4 mW


