=================================================================================
                        THERMAL MANAGEMENT REQUIREMENTS
=================================================================================

Heat Dissipation:
  @ 25°C ambient: 234.5 mW requires cooling
  @ 55°C ambient: 312.4 mW (with 30°C rise) - needs heatsink
  @ 85°C ambient: 378.6 mW (junction limited)

Recommended Cooling:
  Thermal vias: 8x8 array under device (0.5mm diameter)
  Heatsink: Not required for 25°C ambient continuous
  Forced air: Recommended for reliable operation >50°C ambient

Junction Temperature Margin:
  @ 25°C: 27.6°C margin (ACCEPTABLE)
  @ 50°C: 2.6°C margin (CRITICAL)
  Status: Monitor temperature in field


=================================================================================
                        DECOUPLING CAPACITOR RECOMMENDATION
=================================================================================

VCORE Supply (1.2V):
  Bulk capacitors: 4x 47µF ceramic (low ESR, X7R)
  Bypass capacitors: 32x 100nF distributed (every 6mm)
  Total capacitance: 188µF + 3.2µF = 191.2µF

VDSP Supply (2.5V):
  Bulk capacitors: 2x 22µF ceramic
  Bypass capacitors: 16x 100nF
  Total capacitance: 44µF + 1.6µF = 45.6µF

VCCIO Supply (3.3V):
  Bulk capacitors: 2x 10µF
  Bypass capacitors: 16x 100nF per bank (8 banks)
  Total capacitance per bank: 12µF + 1.6µF = 13.6µF

VCCAUX Supply:
  Bypass capacitors: 8x 100nF
  Total capacitance: 0.8µF


